N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4823.1 - License required

State Regulations

No person, firm or corporation shall sell, lease or other
furnish electronic bingo aids to any authorized organization for use in
conjunction with the conduct or licensed bingo games without having first
obtained a license therefore as provided in article 14-H of the General

Municipal Law and this Chapter. Notes
